playwright_tests/
# Ignore docs, but keep the canonical OpenAPI spec: api/views/docs.py
# serves _docs/openapi.json at runtime (/api/openapi.json). Excluding it
# makes /api/docs 500 in prod (issue #862). _docs/* + negation re-includes
# only that one file; using _docs/* (not _docs/) keeps the negation working
# on legacy builders too, since a fully-excluded dir can't re-include a child.
_docs/*
!_docs/openapi.json
specs/
.claude/
